SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t0."EmployeeId", t0."SystemRoleId", t0."Id", t0.description, t0.role_name, t0."SystemRoleId0", t0."PermissionId", t0."Id0", t0."PermissionCode", t0."PermissionName"
FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber"
    FROM employees AS e
    WHERE e."Email" = @__email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"
    FROM employees_systemroles_mapping AS e0
    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT s0."SystemRoleId", s0."PermissionId", p."Id", p."PermissionCode", p."PermissionName"
        FROM systemrole_permissions AS s0
        INNER JOIN permissions AS p ON s0."PermissionId" = p."Id"
    ) AS t1 ON s."Id" = t1."SystemRoleId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EmployeeId", t0."SystemRoleId", t0."Id", t0."SystemRoleId0", t0."PermissionId"

FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber"
    FROM employees AS e
    WHERE e."Email" = @__email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"
    FROM employees_systemroles_mapping AS e0
    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT s0."SystemRoleId", s0."PermissionId", p."Id", p."PermissionCode", p."PermissionName"
        FROM systemrole_permissions AS s0
        INNER JOIN permissions AS p ON s0."PermissionId" = p."Id"
    ) AS t1 ON s."Id" = t1."SystemRoleId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EmployeeId", t0."SystemRoleId", t0."Id", t0."SystemRoleId0", t0."PermissionId"

2025-01-04 13:45:40.722 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (52ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"

    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"

    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1

) AS t

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."AppraiseeScore", t."AppraiserScore", t."CycleId0", t."EmployeeId0", t."PerformanceBucket", t."Id1", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id2", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id3", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a1."Id", a1."AppraiseeComment", a1."AppraiseeRating", a1."AppraiserComment", a1."AppraiserRating", a1."FeedbackId", a1."QuestionId", a1."Status", a1."Artifact_FilePath", a1."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a1
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a1."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1

) AS t

    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t."Id3", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", a0."Id" AS "Id0", a0."AppraiseeScore", a0."AppraiserScore", a0."CycleId" AS "CycleId0", a0."EmployeeId" AS "EmployeeId0", a0."PerformanceBucket", e."Id" AS "Id1", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id2", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id3", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    LEFT JOIN appraisal_summaries AS a0 ON a."SummaryId" = a0."Id"
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    WHERE a1."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-01-04 16:03:05.398 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (31ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    WHERE e."Email" = @__email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT e."Id", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber"
    FROM employees AS e
    WHERE e."Email" = @__email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"
    FROM employees_systemroles_mapping AS e0
    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"

        SELECT s0."SystemRoleId", s0."PermissionId", p."Id", p."PermissionCode", p."PermissionName"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."Id" = @__feedbackId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName", d0."Id" AS "Id3", d0."DepartmentId", d0."PerformanceFactorId", d0."Weightage" AS "Weightage0"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN department_performancefactor AS d0 ON p0."Id" = d0."PerformanceFactorId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1", t0."Id2"

    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_form AS a
    WHERE a."EmployeeRoleId" = @__employeeRoleId_0 AND a."Status" = @__status_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1

) AS t

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."Status", t0."AppraisalFormId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Id", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."CreatedAt", a."EmployeeRoleId", a."Status"
    FROM appraisal_form AS a
    WHERE a."EmployeeRoleId" = @__employeeRoleId_0 AND a."Status" = @__status_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."AppraisalFormId", a0."QuestionId", q."Id", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status"
    FROM appraisal_form_question AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AppraisalFormId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."AppraisalFormId", t0."QuestionId"

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2025-01-04 17:33:17.694 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (41ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."CreatedAt", a."EmployeeRoleId", a."Status"
    FROM appraisal_form AS a
    WHERE a."EmployeeRoleId" = @__employeeRoleId_0 AND a."Status" = @__status_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."AppraisalFormId", a0."QuestionId", q."Id", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AppraisalFormId"

    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"
    FROM employees_systemroles_mapping AS e0
    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"

        INNER JOIN permissions AS p ON s0."PermissionId" = p."Id"
    ) AS t1 ON s."Id" = t1."SystemRoleId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EmployeeId", t0."SystemRoleId", t0."Id", t0."SystemRoleId0", t0."PermissionId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1

    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."CreatedAt", a."EmployeeRoleId", a."Status"
    FROM appraisal_form AS a
    WHERE a."EmployeeRoleId" = @__employeeRoleId_0 AND a."Status" = @__status_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."AppraisalFormId", a0."QuestionId", q."Id", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AppraisalFormId"

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"

    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT e."Id", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber"
    FROM employees AS e
    WHERE e."Email" = @__email_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT e0."EmployeeId", e0."SystemRoleId", s."Id", s.description, s.role_name, t1."SystemRoleId" AS "SystemRoleId0", t1."PermissionId", t1."Id" AS "Id0", t1."PermissionCode", t1."PermissionName"
    FROM employees_systemroles_mapping AS e0
    INNER JOIN system_roles AS s ON e0."SystemRoleId" = s."Id"
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT s0."SystemRoleId", s0."PermissionId", p."Id", p."PermissionCode", p."PermissionName"
        FROM systemrole_permissions AS s0
        INNER JOIN permissions AS p ON s0."PermissionId" = p."Id"
    ) AS t1 ON s."Id" = t1."SystemRoleId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."EmployeeId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."EmployeeId", t0."SystemRoleId", t0."Id", t0."SystemRoleId0", t0."PermissionId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"

    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    WHERE a."EmployeeRoleId" = @__employeeRoleId_0 AND a."Status" = @__status_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."AppraisalFormId", a0."QuestionId", q."Id", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AppraisalFormId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    LIMIT 1
) AS t

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."AppraisalFormId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"

    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."Id" = @__feedbackId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName", d0."Id" AS "Id3", d0."DepartmentId", d0."PerformanceFactorId", d0."Weightage" AS "Weightage0"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    LEFT JOIN department_performancefactor AS d0 ON p0."Id" = d0."PerformanceFactorId"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1", t0."Id2"

SELECT t."Id", t."AppraiserId", t."CreatedAt", t."CycleId", t."EmployeeId", t."Status", t."SummaryId", t."Id0", t."CreatedOn", t."Email", t."EmployeeRoleId", t."FirstName", t."IsActive", t."LastName", t."ModifiedOn", t."PasswordHash", t."PhoneNumber", t."Id1", t."departmentId", t."EmployeeRoleCode", t."HierarchyLevel", t."RoleName", t."Id2", t."DepartmentName", t0."Id", t0."AppraiseeComment", t0."AppraiseeRating", t0."AppraiserComment", t0."AppraiserRating", t0."FeedbackId", t0."QuestionId", t0."Status", t0."Artifact_FilePath", t0."Artifact_FileType", t0."Id0", t0."PerformanceIndicatorId", t0."QuestionText", t0."Status0", t0."Id1", t0."FactorId", t0."IndicatorName", t0."Weightage", t0."Id2", t0."FactorName"
FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"

    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'

FROM (
    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"
    FROM appraisal_feedbacks AS a
    INNER JOIN employees AS e ON a."EmployeeId" = e."Id"
    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_indicator AS p ON q."PerformanceIndicatorId" = p."Id"
    INNER JOIN performance_factor AS p0 ON p."FactorId" = p0."Id"
    WHERE a0."Status" = 'Pending'
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t."Id1", t."Id2", t0."Id", t0."Id0", t0."Id1"

    INNER JOIN employee_roles AS e0 ON e."EmployeeRoleId" = e0."Id"
    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."EmployeeId" = @__employeeId_0 AND a."CycleId" = @__cycleId_1

    SELECT a."Id", a."AppraiserId", a."CreatedAt", a."CycleId", a."EmployeeId", a."Status", a."SummaryId", e."Id" AS "Id0", e."CreatedOn", e."Email", e."EmployeeRoleId", e."FirstName", e."IsActive", e."LastName", e."ModifiedOn", e."PasswordHash", e."PhoneNumber", e0."Id" AS "Id1", e0."departmentId", e0."EmployeeRoleCode", e0."HierarchyLevel", e0."RoleName", d."Id" AS "Id2", d."DepartmentName"

    INNER JOIN department AS d ON e0."departmentId" = d."Id"
    WHERE a."Id" = @__feedbackId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT a0."Id", a0."AppraiseeComment", a0."AppraiseeRating", a0."AppraiserComment", a0."AppraiserRating", a0."FeedbackId", a0."QuestionId", a0."Status", a0."Artifact_FilePath", a0."Artifact_FileType", q."Id" AS "Id0", q."PerformanceIndicatorId", q."QuestionText", q."Status" AS "Status0", p."Id" AS "Id1", p."FactorId", p."IndicatorName", p."Weightage", p0."Id" AS "Id2", p0."FactorName", d0."Id" AS "Id3", d0."DepartmentId", d0."PerformanceFactorId", d0."Weightage" AS "Weightage0"
    FROM appraisal_feedback_details AS a0
    INNER JOIN question AS q ON a0."QuestionId" = q."Id"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."FeedbackId"
